      "span_text": "The samples that were combined to form the juxtaposed F* (xI, H, K) group in the previous study were further genotyped in this study for P130 (rs17250887), P124(rs17315772) and P209 (rs17315835) and assigned to respective hg-J and hg-I following the Y chromosome consortium (YCC 2008) nomenclature. [CITATION_1]"
